title: Pain vs Suffering
itunes:title: Pain vs Suffering
description:
Episode 285 - Pain is inevitable but suffering is a choice. Pain is something that happened to you in your past, suffering is keeping that pain with you in the present. In this episode, I teach you how to stop suffering and allowing your suffering from holding you back.
